c: 3
v: 199
t: "Mazima ddala mu Bantu ab'aweebwa ekitabo mulimu abantu abakkiriza Katonda nebakkiriza ebyassibwa gyemuli, n’ebyassibwa gyebali, bagondera Katonda ebigambo bya Katonda tebabitundamu muwendo mutono, abo balina okufuna empeera yaabwe ewa Mukama omulabirizi waabwe, mazima Katonda tagenda kukaluubirirwa kubala"